&lt;p data-section-id=&quot;jpe99q&quot; data-start=&quot;345&quot; data-end=&quot;356&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ABOUT US&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;358&quot; data-end=&quot;533&quot;&gt;We believe early childhood education is where everything begins - first friendships, first discoveries, and the foundation for a lifetime of learning.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;535&quot; data-end=&quot;789&quot;&gt;Our schools are built around creating safe, nurturing, and engaging environments where children can grow with confidence and curiosity. Every member of our team plays an important role in shaping meaningful experiences for children and families each day.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;791&quot; data-end=&quot;927&quot;&gt;We are always looking for passionate, caring, and dedicated individuals who want to make a difference through early childhood education.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-section-id=&quot;1aogafb&quot; data-start=&quot;929&quot; data-end=&quot;943&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHY JOIN US&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;945&quot; data-end=&quot;1072&quot;&gt;Working in one of our schools means being part of a supportive team that values collaboration, growth, and purpose-driven work.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1074&quot; data-end=&quot;1271&quot;&gt;Whether you work in the classroom, school leadership, enrollment, or school support operations, you’ll help create a positive environment where children feel safe, supported, and inspired to learn.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1273&quot; data-end=&quot;1395&quot;&gt;We invest in our people through training, development, mentorship, and opportunities for career growth across our schools.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-section-id=&quot;1szwgfp&quot; data-start=&quot;1397&quot; data-end=&quot;1421&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHO WE’RE LOOKING FOR&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1423&quot; data-end=&quot;1453&quot;&gt;We’re seeking individuals who:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul data-start=&quot;1454&quot; data-end=&quot;1773&quot;&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;3c8gbi&quot; data-start=&quot;1454&quot; data-end=&quot;1522&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Are passionate about working with children and supporting families&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;j209jv&quot; data-start=&quot;1523&quot; data-end=&quot;1581&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Create positive and supportive relationships with others&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;gf7ktq&quot; data-start=&quot;1582&quot; data-end=&quot;1636&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Lead with integrity, professionalism, and compassion&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1snb87p&quot; data-start=&quot;1637&quot; data-end=&quot;1676&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Thrive in a team-oriented environment&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;gb2thy&quot; data-start=&quot;1677&quot; data-end=&quot;1717&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Value safety, learning, and excellence&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1y46k7q&quot; data-start=&quot;1718&quot; data-end=&quot;1773&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Bring a proactive and positive approach to their work&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p data-section-id=&quot;5pxyxr&quot; data-start=&quot;1775&quot; data-end=&quot;1798&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;FUTURE OPPORTUNITIES&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1800&quot; data-end=&quot;1904&quot;&gt;Don’t see a current opening that matches your background or interests? We’d still love to hear from you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1906&quot; data-end=&quot;2128&quot;&gt;Submit your information to be considered for future opportunities across our schools and support teams. As positions become available, our team may contact you regarding roles that align with your experience and interests.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

